summary: I am a natural problem solver with strong analytical skills and a pro-active, hands-on mentality. I have a distinct drive for execution and results and a clear focus on customer satisfaction. I can analyze any problem critically which gives me many facets for solving the problem. Using emotional intelligence, I can build a good team, produce effective result and build lasting relationships with colleagues. I always try to do my work in a sustainable way without doing any harm to the environment and man-kind. I consider myself as a visionary person who likes to grow making his surroundings healthier and happier. I also would like to apply my knowledge in the logistics industry that I learned in my Master program (e.g. sourcing & purchasing, operation management, warehouse management, transportation & distribution, port management, etc.).
